text: Aleksa Striković (born 12 May 1961) is a Serbian chess grandmaster. He won the FR Yugoslavia Chess Championship in 1992, and the South African Open in 2016.http://www.chess- results.com/tnr225994.aspx?lan=1&art;=4&turdet;=YES&flag;=30&wi;=984 He also competed in the 1998 Chess Olympiad for Yugoslavia, finishing on 3.5/7.http://www.chess- results.com/tnr403.aspx?lan=1&art;=20&turdet;=YES&wi;=984&snr;=19 ==References== Category:1961 births Category:Living people Category:Serbian chess players Category:Chess grandmasters Category:Chess Olympiad competitors
